---
title: Beginner Abacus Fundamentals Course

description: Beginner abacus fundamentals course for bead values, reading numbers on the abacus, add and subtract questions. Printable worksheets increase with difficulty.
---


<content class="course" id="beginner-page">
	<section>
		<div>
		 	<h1>Beginner Abacus Fundamentals Course</h1>	
		 	<p>This is the first of three courses that aim to teach multi-digit number calculations. The beginner course gives students a chance to practice <%= link_to 'reading numbers on the abacus', '/progressive-abacus/skills', :relative => true %> while carrying out the most simple <%= link_to 'direct movements', '/progressive-abacus/skills#direct-movement', :relative => true %>. It begins with direct-4 questions that only involve the bottom four beads and progresses to direct-9 questions that use bottom and top beads.</p>	
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="test">
		<div class="pure-g levels-button" role="list">
			<div class="pure-u-1 pure-u-sm-1-3 press-button">
				<button class="modal-button beginner" type="button" role="button" aria-label="beginner level 1: direct 4">
					<h4>Level 1</h4>
					<p>Direct-4: &nbspsingle digit</p>
				</button>
			</div>
			<div class="pure-u-1 pure-u-sm-1-3 press-button">
				<button class="modal-button beginner" type="button" role="button" aria-label="beginner level 2: direct 4">
					<h4>Level 2</h4>
					<p>Direct-4: &nbspdouble digit</p>
				</button>
			</div>
			<div class="pure-u-1 pure-u-sm-1-3 press-button">
				<button class="modal-button beginner" type="button" role="button" aria-label="beginner level 3: direct 4">
					<h4>Level 3</h4>
					<p>Direct-4: &nbsptriple digit</p>
				</button>
			</div>
			<div class="pure-u-1 pure-u-sm-1-3 press-button">
				<button class="modal-button beginner" type="button" role="button" aria-label="beginner level 4: direct 9">
					<h4>Level 4</h4>
					<p>Direct-9: &nbspsingle digit</p>
				</button>
			</div>
			<div class="pure-u-1 pure-u-sm-1-3 press-button">
				<button class="modal-button beginner" type="button" role="button" aria-label="beginner level 5: direct 9">
					<h4>Level 5</h4>
					<p>Direct-9: &nbspdouble digit</p>
				</button>
			</div>
			<div class="pure-u-1 pure-u-sm-1-3 press-button">
				<button class="modal-button beginner" type="button" role="button" aria-label="beginner level 6: direct 9">
					<h4>Level 6</h4>
					<p>Direct-9: &nbsptriple digit</p>
				</button>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section>
		<div class="arrow">
			<div class="arrow-right">
				<a href="/progressive-abacus/intermediate" title="intermediate abacus fundamentals course">
					<h4>Intermediate Course</h4>
					<%= image_tag 'right_arrow.svg' %>
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</content>

<%= partial 'partials/modal' %>

